code: @Before public void setUp() throws Exception {     if (!valueStateDesc.isSerializerInitialized()) {         valueStateDesc.initializeSerializerUnlessSet(new ExecutionConfig()).     }     valueState = ImmutableValueState.createState(valueStateDesc, ByteBuffer.allocate(Long.BYTES).putLong(42L).array()). }
@Test(expected = UnsupportedOperationException.class) public void testUpdate() throws IOException {     long value = valueState.value().     assertEquals(42L, value).     valueState.update(54L). }
@Test(expected = UnsupportedOperationException.class) public void testClear() throws IOException {     long value = valueState.value().     assertEquals(42L, value).     valueState.clear(). }
